    "`-` Apply SSA to Testsignal 1\n",
    "   - Reference: Golyandina, N., Korobeynikov, A., Shlemov, A., & Usevich, K. (2013). Multivariate and 2D extensions of singular spectrum analysis with the Rssa package. arXiv preprint arXiv:1309.5050.\n",
    "\n",
    "`-` Window size is 64*64"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "16620da5-903d-4037-b72b-990bf11a5802",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "`-` The window size can be interpreted as a multiscale parameter.\n",
    " - Small window size: Focusing on local changes, advantageous for judging sudden changes in signals; Suitable for analyzing partial normal time series\n",
    " - Large window size: Focus on global structure; Suitable for analyzing stationary time series"
   ]
  },
