    "`-` It is difficult to separate the global structure (low-freq)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "131c8cf5-1004-4bbf-8e24-c5ca7e25f433",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "> Note: small window size -> It can't separate global structure (=low freq) properly -> LF_hat contains some high-frequency signal"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "a17cae28-b00b-4b60-9bca-0f7d76d43390",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2D PCA"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "f0820b1a-3aef-415e-9815-e73cfb804935",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "`-` Reference of 2D PCA is as follows\n",
    " - Yang, J., Zhang, D., Frangi, A. F., & Yang, J. Y. (2004). Two-dimensional PCA: a new approach to appearance-based face representation and recognition. IEEE transactions on pattern analysis and machine intelligence, 26(1), 131-137.\n",
    " - ($\\ast$) 2D-PCA는 구현된 코드를 찾기 어려워 일단은 임시로 제가 위 논문의 내용을 직접 구현하여 시뮬레이션 하였습니다. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 211,
   "id": "0d1c9a09-6c2a-412b-ae12-5f6302c6eaa8",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "A=cosmeanf\n",
    "G=t(A-mean(A))%*%(A-mean(A)) \n",
    "svd_<-svd(G)"
   ]
  },
